rows.label: tlk44200181_02_msg0001
rows.name: So we're not related to Adel then?

rows.label: tlk44200181_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Mama, Papa, Grandma, and Granddad
were all terribly upset when
they found out about that.

rows.label: tlk44200181_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But doesn't this mean
that Luxuria's free now?

rows.label: tlk44200181_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I want to visit all the other
countries and find the
prettiest-looking places!

rows.label: tlk44200181_02_msg0005
rows.name:
There are so many exciting things
to see and do in the world... So
why do adults always look so sad?
